乏 128GB 以上的存储选项。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>与此同时，Pixel Buds A-Series 即使以通常的价格也<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-buds-a-series-review-160054961.html">令人印象深刻</a>。它们提供均衡的声音、舒适的贴合度和紧密的 Google Assistant 集成（例如翻译对话）。没有无线充电或主动降噪功能，但在这个价格级别中这是预期的。免费的话，它们几乎是无与伦比的。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://subscription.yahoo.net/Newsletter/Preference/sub?b=engadgetdeals&amp;src"><em>订阅 Engadget Deals 时事通讯，</em></a><em>了解最新的科技交易和购买建议。</em></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-7a-bundle-with-pixel-buds-a-series-is-100-off-at-amazon-132623671.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-7a-bundle-with-pixel-buds-a-series-is-100-off-at-amazon-132623671.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e4971863-5414-4733-a81a-946a6f200758</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jun 2023 13:26:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687526200</ingested><modified> 2023-06-23T13:16:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1077" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/2f170730-11c2-11ee-a267-77067fec224d" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></